Race.Name: Urban Renewal
Race.Description: Some say that Davis could never host an open wheel series. But a state-of-the-art pit stop is surely just the kind of public i nvestment that an underprivileged neighborhood needs. So don't think of the track as ''poorly funded''. Those potholes and con crete blocks are the natural obstacles that separate the weeken d racers from the real pros. Lap race for open wheel cars.
